welcome to using the task tracing system.
the system is an Online IT support helpdisk system, which support microsoft windows 2008 domain.
all user must have an account of AD before they use the system. IT stuff should be assigned rights to deal the IT Case.
the system also includes a free radius database, which can be used to control wireless access by freeradius.

  the system depends on ruby-ldap. so  if you want to try, you need install ruby-ldap first.